  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5237346/" class="title-link">有真批评才有真学术</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5237346"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/fengguoyuanye/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1256422-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fengguoyuanye/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">李寅初</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2011-12-30"
      class="main-meta">2011-12-30 21:23:12</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5237346_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                   杨奎松教授是研究中国现当代史的著名学者，其著作深受读者喜爱，多次荣获各项大奖。在当下社会，一个严肃的历史学家的著作，能够获得各方颇为一致的高度赞誉是很难的。我想，这一方面是因为杨教授常常行走在“雷区”，研究课题大都“敏感”，西安事变、中苏关系、土改、镇反等...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">6有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
