          <div id="review_5237346_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5237346_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6513226">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6513226/" class="title-link">当《苦难辉煌》以畅销书的面目出现的时候……</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6513226"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/westwinds/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1001804-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/westwinds/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">西风吹吹</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-01-17"
      class="main-meta">2014-01-17 10:20:03</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6513226_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  当金一南的《苦难辉煌》披着历史纪实作品的外衣出版，并以畅销书的面目摆上书店柜架的时候，需要杨老师这样的史家对其进行剥丝抽茧搬的“批判”，历史特别是近现代史要还原所谓真实很难，但至少不能刻意扭曲，不能不加追索。可惜，严谨的史家注定是孤独和少人理解的。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6513226_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6513226_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





